*[[黃可盈|黃可盈]]：演員、模特兒<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.orientalsunday.hk/216960/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e5%a8%9b%e8%81%9e/%e5%b2%a1%e6%9c%ac%e5%a5%b3%e7%a5%9e-%e5%81%9a%e9%81%8ewaitress-%e9%bb%83%e5%8f%af%e7%9b%88-%ef%bc%9a%e9%83%bd%e4%bf%82%e9%ab%94%e9%a9%97%e5%9a%9f%e5%95%ab%ef%bc%81/|title=岡本女神 做過waitress 黃可盈 ：都係體驗嚟啫！|agency=[[東方新地|東方新地]]|date=2017-07-28|access-date=2019-09-19|archive-date=2019-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923030007/https://www.orientalsunday.hk/216960/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e5%a8%9b%e8%81%9e/%e5%b2%a1%e6%9c%ac%e5%a5%b3%e7%a5%9e-%e5%81%9a%e9%81%8ewaitress-%e9%bb%83%e5%8f%af%e7%9b%88-%ef%bc%9a%e9%83%bd%e4%bf%82%e9%ab%94%e9%a9%97%e5%9a%9f%e5%95%ab%ef%bc%81/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[連綺文|連綺文]]：騷戲劇盟團長伴侶
